OL,3,CBrown and Davey raise tax avoidance
OL,4,Cconcerns after ITV News report on Sky
OL,5,CBet
OL,7,FFormer prime minister Gordon Brown has
OL,8,Fasked MPs on the Treasury Select
OL,9,FCommittee to investigate whether
OL,10,Fbetting firms are exploiting the tax
OL,11,Fsystem.
OL,13,FHis intervention follows ITV News'
OL,14,Frevelation that Flutter Entertainment
OL,15,FPLC has moved the headquarters of Sky
OL,16,FBet to Malta in an attempt to cut its
OL,17,FUK tax bill by tens of millions of
OL,18,Fpounds.
