OL,3,CBrown and Davey raise tax avoidance
OL,4,Cconcerns after ITV News report on Sky
OL,5,CBet
OL,7,FIn a statement, Brown said the report
OL,8,F"raises serious concerns about
OL,9,Fpotential tax avoidance that warrant
OL,10,Fthorough investigation".
OL,12,FThe Treasury Select Committee has
OL,13,Falready been examining the taxation of
OL,14,Fthe betting and gaming industry ahead
OL,15,Fof next week's Budget.
OL,17,FBrown wants the committee to "widen
OL,18,Fits inquiry to include transfer
OL,19,Fpricing, tax avoidance, and the VAT
OL,20,Floophole described by Dan Neidle of
OL,21,FTax Policy Associates".
