OL,3,CBrown and Davey raise tax avoidance
OL,4,Cconcerns after ITV News report on Sky
OL,5,CBet
OL,7,FEarlier at Prime Minister's Questions,
OL,8,Fthe prime minister avoided answering a
OL,9,Fquestion from the leader of the
OL,10,FLiberal Democrats, Sir Ed Davey, about
OL,11,Fwhether the government would act to
OL,12,Fstop gambling companies shifting
OL,13,Fprofits offshore to avoid UK
OL,14,Fcorporation tax.
OL,16,FDavey said that online gambling firms
OL,17,Fare taking record revenues of over
OL,18,F#7bn per year.
