OL,3,CBrown and Davey raise tax avoidance
OL,4,Cconcerns after ITV News report on Sky
OL,5,CBet
OL,7,FAccording to Dan Neidle, the tax
OL,8,Fspecialist working with ITV News, a
OL,9,Fcompany based in Malta can pay an
OL,10,Feffective corporation tax rate of as
OL,11,Flittle as 5%, compared with 25% in the
OL,12,FUK.
OL,14,FBased on Sky Bet's profits last year
OL,15,F(filed by Hestview Ltd), that would
OL,16,Frepresent a potential saving of up to
OL,17,F#31 million.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
