OL,5,CBet
OL,7,FNeidle also believes Flutter could
OL,8,Fexploit a VAT loophole that would have
OL,9,Freduced the VAT paid on Sky Bet's
OL,10,Fmarketing budget last year by as much
OL,11,Fas #24 million.
OL,13,FFlutter admits the relocation to Malta
OL,14,F"will have some tax implications" and
OL,15,Fhas not disputed Neidle's calculations.
OL,17,FIn a post on X this morning, Neidle
OL,18,Fdescribed the VAT arrangement as
OL,19,F"improper".
