OL,5,CBet
OL,7,FA Flutter UKI spokesperson said:
OL,8,F"Flutter is one of the biggest
OL,9,Ftaxpayers in the UK and will continue
OL,10,Fto be so. As part of a global business
OL,11,Flisted in New York, we continually
OL,12,Freview where we invest as we strive to
OL,13,Fremain competitive. We are confident
OL,14,Fwe operate in accordance with tax law
OL,15,Facross all our jurisdictions."
OL,17,FThe Treasury declined to comment.
OL,19,FNumber 10 and The Betting and Gaming
OL,20,FCouncil have been approached for
OL,21,Fcomment.
